---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About" description="Justin Helmer — Principal Engineer at Webflow.">
  <h1 class="page-heading">About</h1>
  <div class="about-text">
    <p>Principal Engineer at Webflow. I work on AI infrastructure, developer tooling, and the internal systems that the product runs on. Most of what I build isn't visible to end users — it's the layers that make everything else possible.</p>
    <p>Before Webflow: Intellimize, Macy's (mobile platform), and Cal Poly SLO. I've been writing software professionally for 17 years.</p>
    <p>I think in systems. I care about composability, clear interfaces, and building things that hold up under pressure. This site is my notebook and sandbox.</p>
  </div>
</Base>

<style>
  .about-text {
    max-width: 560px;
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .about-text p + p {
    margin-top: 1.5em;
  }
</style>
